com.solana.digitalassetlinks.StatementMatcher
public class StatementMatcher extends Object

      Apply this StatementMatcher against the specified
      Parameters:

    • createWebStatementMatcher

      public static StatementMatcher createWebStatementMatcher(@NonNull String relation, @Nullable URI site)
      Create a StatementMatcher for the AssetLinksGrammar.GRAMMAR_NAMESPACE_WEB namespace
      Parameters:
      relation - the AssetLinksGrammar.GRAMMAR_RELATION to match
      site - if non-null, the AssetLinksGrammar.GRAMMAR_WEB_SITE to match. This will be validated against the rules for the web domain.
      Returns:
      a StatementMatcher
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if site is non-null and fails validation

    • createAndroidAppStatementMatcher

      public static StatementMatcher createAndroidAppStatementMatcher(@NonNull String relation, @Nullable String packageName, @Nullable String sha256CertFingerprint)
      Create a StatementMatcher for the AssetLinksGrammar.GRAMMAR_NAMESPACE_ANDROID_APP namespace
      Parameters:
      relation - the AssetLinksGrammar.GRAMMAR_RELATION to match
      packageName - if non-null, the AssetLinksGrammar.GRAMMAR_ANDROID_APP_PACKAGE_NAME to match. This will be validated against the rules for the android_app domain.
      sha256CertFingerprint - if non-null, the AssetLinksGrammar.GRAMMAR_ANDROID_APP_SHA256_CERT_FINGERPRINTS to match. This will be validated against the rules for the android_app domain.
      Returns:
      a StatementMatcher
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if packageName is non-null and fails validation, or if sha256CertFingerprint is non-null and fails validation.
